e":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"信果個都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8f0df12ffa9a430a09654be6fe1b15a6ef042f","tid":390980,"uid":27713,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:18:56.000Z","msg":"同過佢玩幾次 女係有 但真係無人so佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為同場個個都有錢 靚仔過佢又有<br />\n高過佢嘅又有"},{"pid":"cf29019fb648b88838080931caef207fc6ad1e7a","tid":390980,"uid":32437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:21:32.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦鍾培生"},{"pid":"172b6e37694123bf4e3bf3ebb21b322848eef01e","tid":390980,"uid":26322,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮乜野洗底<br />\n中學就食唔少𡃁模  搞埋啲淫賤船p  大把女埋身</blockquote><br />\n洗底技巧差左少少<br />\n<br />\n都唔知邊個教佢咁做，炒左佢啦鍾生<br />\n<br />\n比幾球出黎做下善事扮下野，洗底仲快啦，你又唔係比唔起"},{"pid":"594d77099c3867664b97e9851f036deab1ca5133","tid":390980,"uid":7805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扮乜野洗底<br />\n中學就食唔少𡃁模  搞埋啲淫賤船p  大把女埋身</blockquote><br />\n洗底技巧差左少少<br />\n<br />\n都唔知邊個教佢咁做，炒左佢啦鍾生<br />\n<br />\n比幾球出黎做下善事扮下野，洗底仲快啦，你又唔係比唔起</blockquote><br />\n心痛呀嘛，性價比唔高"},{"pid":"ef44fcb279dac873fdbed312e732e5ec57ec4042","tid":390980,"uid":31397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"條仆街真係好矮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8113f372259b3eec9b3a110e8bd8f8d70ff5ef5e","tid":390980,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"扮經驗少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只是方便Ｄ女送上門"},{"pid":"ce1d5ef9970a5850f8e140758190ddc0e61d6759","tid":390980,"uid":111814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"有錢搵打手出篇鱔稿真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\"